  Chha-put-to chap8-ni5-cheng5 , ti7 Jit8-pun2 e5 chng-sia7 u7 chit8-lang5 khi3 hioh ti7 hit kheh-tiam3, ti7 hia chiah8 ho2-mih8 , ia7 toa3 ho2 sou2-chai7 , chhiaN2 lang5 lai5 chhoe-siau chhiuN3-khek, lim-chiu2 khoai3-lok8 chit8-tiuN5. Kau3 beh khun3 e5 si5 , hoan-hu3 tiam3-chu2 , kah i bin5-a2-chai3 11 tiam2-cheng tioh8 kio3 i chhiN2. Hit e5 tiam3-chu2 chiu7 chiau3 i e5 oe7 , kau3 hit-si5 jip8-khi3 beh kio3 ; khoaN3-kiN3 bin5-chhng5-cheng5 soan-chhut chit8-ki hou5-li5 boe2, hut-jian5 kiaN kau3 be7-kou3--tit , sui5-si5 chau2-chhut-lai5 , phah-sng3 hit-e5 lang5-kheh tek-khak si7 iau-koai3. Ka-ti7 teh siuN7--kioh m7-ku2 u7 hoan-hu3 i , na7 bo5 kio3 i, iu7 kiaN-liau2 hou7 i koe3-siau3 khian3-chek. Kou-put-chiong koh-chai3 jip8-khi3 , chiu7 khoaN3 hit-e5 lang5-kheh che7 ti7 bin5-chhng5, teh chiah8 hun. Hit-e5 lang5-kheh khoaN3-kiN3 tiam3-chu2 sim-sin5 tah-hiahN , chiu7 mng7 i , Li2 u7 jip8-lai5 chia khoaN3-kiN3 saN2-hoe3 ? Tai7-seng tiam3-chu2 m7-kaN2 kong2 , kan-ta the-si5 kong2 , Bo5--ah , Bo5--ah！ Hit-e5 lang5-kheh koh kong2 , Li2 tek-khak u7 khoaN3-kiN3 sim2-mih8--leh ; li2 tioh8 beng5-beng5 ka7 goa2 kong2. Hit-e5 tiam3-chu2 jian5-au7 chiah ka7 i kong2 lau2-sit8 , Goa2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit8-ki hou5-li5 boe2. Hit-e5 lang5-kheh chiah in3 i kong2, Hm7-hm7 , li2 taN i2-keng u7 khoaN3-kiN3, goa2 put-hong5 sit8-chai7 ka7 li2 kong2 . Goa2 chiu7-si7 lau7 hou5-li5 , siong5-si5 tiam3 ti7 soaN--nih8 ; chit-tiap8 lai5 chia si7 beh pan7 tai7-chi3 . Li2 sou2-khoaN3 sou2-thiaN chit-ho7 su7 , li2 toan3-toan3 m7-thang ka7 lang5 kong2 . Li2 na7 ko2-jian5 an2-ni , siok8-hou7 li2 put-lun7 u7 chiN5 he7 ti7 bio7--nih8 , goa2 beh hou7 li2 ke chit8-poe7 . Kong2 liau2 chiu7 cho3 i khi2-sin, long2 bo5 poaN3-iN5 sou2-hui3 hou7 i ; hit e5 tiam3-chu2 ia7 m7-kaN2 ka7 i theh8 . Theng3-hau7 kau3 bin5-a2-chai3 chiu7 chin-chiaN3 theh8 50 chiN5 he7 ti7 bio7--nih8 chhi3-khoaN3 ; kau3 au7--jit8 lai5 khoaN3, ko2-jian5 u7 piN3 chit8-pah . He7 kau3 kui2-na7 jit8 ,iu5-goan5 si7 an2-ni , chai7 hit-e5 tiam3-c